 Dermal Profile Analysis Using the NMR-MOUSE@highlight

The determination of fluid status in dialysis patients is a major clinical problem.

 In this study the NMR-MOUSE is used to determine if it can be used to non-invasively determine hydration status of the skin.

 This evaluation will be performed in dialysis patients and healthy volunteers.

